    'description' => 'Fetch the current top stories from the HackerNews API (Firebase-based, no API key required). Retrieves top story IDs, then fetches full details (title, URL, score, author, comments, timestamp) for each. Can persist to SQLite for historical tracking. Uses PHP streams for all network calls. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data. First community/social data source in the ecosystem.',
    'parameters' => 
